[2;36m│[0m ### Key Findings:                                                            [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 1. **Scripts ARE executing** - evidenced by error messages appearing with    [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m `error_star.png`                                                             [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 2. **The alert hook is extremely persistent** - It catches alert() calls     [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m from:                                                                        [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m    - Main window                                                             [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m    - Script injection                                                        [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m    - srcdoc iframes                                                          [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m    - Dynamically created iframes                                             [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m    - window.open() new windows                                               [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m    - frames[] array                                                          [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m    - setTimeout with string                                                  [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m    - Object.getPrototypeOf                                                   [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 3. **Impactful findings:**                                                   [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m    - srcdoc iframes execute JavaScript but inherit parent's hooked alert     [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m    - window.open() also inherits the same hook                               [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m    - Prototype-chain access is still blocked                                 [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m    - The hook appears to be applied globally before any script execution     [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 4. **Pattern observed:**                                                     [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m    - "Oops! You did an alert with TypeError: Attempting to change the setter [2;36m│[0m
