[2;36m│[0m ### Next Steps:                                                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m Since iframe/window context bypasses don't work, potential next approaches:  [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 1. Try prototype pollution to redefine `alert` before the hook is applied    [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 2. Try accessing alert from a different prototype (e.g., EventTarget)        [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 3. Try `fetch()` or `XMLHttpRequest` with data exfiltration instead of alert [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 4. Try `document.write()` to create a fresh document context                 [2;36m│[0m
