3. Test accessing alert through opener window: opener && opener.alert
4. Test window.frames and window.self references
5. Test accessing alert via constructor: window.constructor.prototype.alert
6. Test nested window references: top.parent.alert, parent.top.alert
7. Try different reference methods: window["ale"+"rt"], self["alert"], this["alert"]

